<template>

  <v-col  cols="2.7">
    <v-autocomplete
        v-model="collegeValue"
        :items="collegeItem"
        :loading="isLoading"
        dense
        filled
        label="学院"
    ></v-autocomplete>
  </v-col>
  <v-col cols="2.7">
    <v-autocomplete
        v-model="ClassValue"
        :items='ClassItem'
        :loading="isLoading"
        dense
        filled
        label="班级"
        no-data-text="请选择学院"
    ></v-autocomplete>
  </v-col>
  <v-col cols="2.8">
    <v-autocomplete
        v-model="StuValue"
        :items="StuItem"
        :loading="isLoading"
        dense
        filled
        label="学生"
        no-data-text="请选择班级"
    ></v-autocomplete>
  </v-col>
</template>

<script>
export default {
name: "SelectionBar"
}
</script>

<style scoped>

</style>
